Class BinarySearchTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>

java.lang.Object
BinaryTree<E>
BinarySearchTree<E>
Type Parameters:
E - Data type that BST holds. It must extend comparable class.
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, SearchTree<E>
Direct Known Subclasses:
BinarySearchTreeWithRotate
public class BinarySearchTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>
extends BinaryTree<E>
implements SearchTree<E>
A data structure that holds data in a sorted and hierarchical way. Implements search tree interface and extends binary tree class.
